key west’s best kept
secret
A Moment In Time
Tucked behind the famous A&B Lobster House, this speakeasy-style cocktail bar has been a local hideout since the late 1940s.
A true escape from the madness of Key West, take a load off as you sip a crisp martini and settle into a soft leather club chair while jazz floats through the air.
Menus
Drinks
Our selection of cocktails, wine, beer & spirits.
DRINK MENU
Food
Available from A&B Lobster House, everyday until 10pm.
A&B LOBSTER MENU
Hours
Open Daily
5pm – 11pm

IT STARTS AT ZERO
Where Front Street meets the water at the
famous Key West Bight. Look for the zero and
glance to your right …
2.
STAIRWAY TO HEAVEN
Follow the beautifully tiled
staircase up to the balcony …
3.
UP THE RABBIT HOLE
Signs will point the way until
finally …
4.
B MARKS THE SPOT
Welcome to Berlin’s. Check your
inhibitions at the door.
